title: BEILINFuel dispensers with 4 displays
short_description:
Characteristics: 

Model: US-XC-BL2112Z

  • Flow rate: 45 L/min (2 product - 2 nozzle - 4 display).
  • 2 x Motor 220 V/0.75 KW.
  • 2 x Vane pump. 
  • 2 x Flow meter. 
  • 2 x Nozzle.
  • 2 x Solenoid valve.
  • 4 x display board (886 type). 
  • 2 x Metal Keyboard.
  • This equipment is designed for filling all types of gasoline in Uzbekistan (80/91/92/95).

  • Parrakli nasos 2 ta.
  • Oqim o'lchagich 2 ta.
  • Benzin quyish shlanki 2 ta
  • Solenoid klapani 2 ta.
  • Displey paneli 4 ta (886 turi).ac
  • Metall klaviatura 2 ta.
  • Mazkur uskunamiz O’zbekistondagi barcha benzin turlarini quyish uchun mo’ljallangan (80/91/92/95).
